{"about_the_game":"Unleash your creativity with staples of the hairdressing trade \u2013 see how much a simple haircut can change a person!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330560/extras/HD_HEADER_1.gif?t=1737843879\" /><br><br>Experiment with colors and layering. Don\u2019t forget about haircare \u2013 wash  hair, shampoo using the best products, dry them and go through the whole hairstyling process step by step. <br>Balayage, perm or highlights \u2013 the creation choice is up to you!<br>Improve your styling skills and meet your customers expectations.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330560/extras/HD_HEADER_2.gif?t=1737843879\" /><br><br>Aim for the top! Expand your empire and become a hairdressing mogul. Buy and renovate your salon, hire new employees, and learn a few tricks for your customers' satisfaction. Stay up to date with current trends and purchase new products for the most discerning customer - the higher your rating, the more you earn. Don't rest on your laurels and join the hair of fame.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330560/extras/HD_HEADER_4.gif?t=1737843879\" /><br><br>With Hairdresser Simulator you'll get various mechanics and features which will help you in your career.<br>Prepare your salon, grab your scissors and get ready to cut!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330560/extras/HD_HEADER_3.gif?t=1737843879\" /><br><br>Straight, curly, or maybe you\u2019d like bangs to complete a chic look? In Hairdresser, you have the opportunity to experiment with your own appearance - no scissors required! Upload a photo, and Hairdresser Simulator will transform it into a model ready for hair makeovers. Change your look or try out a new hairstyle, sandbox mode provides you with endless possibilities!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Design your own character or upload a portrait photo - make them look like you or a favorite celebrity.<br></li><li>9 salons to make your own - buy them up, improve them with your unique touch and rake in the money.<br></li><li>Renovate your salon, paint the walls and decorate as you please;<br></li><li>Treat your customers right with 10 distinct hairdressing actions: washing, shampooing, drying, brushing, cutting, dyeing and more. And that\u2019s just what you can do before you start styling.<br></li><li>Take control of your customers\u2019 hair with 11 hairdressing tools such as: scissors, razor, brush, hair straightener, curler, dryer, and more!<br></li><li>Manage your salon - from economics to the dirty floor. Somebody has to make sure there\u2019s a decent profit margin\u2026 And make sure your workplace is clean and welcoming - and that person is you.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Let's get down to business","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1330560/d02d0f0cf8e6c26b66d4b38b93a6448c5ab1a077.jpg"},{"name":"Another pair of scissors","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1330560/611c9909f5e5925c99d9ac9206535a5034b52e3f.jpg"},{"name":"The Hairmaster","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1330560/86a60de8bd76937e1c0c11ae6fa298f3ebfda425.jpg"},{"name":"Heeerrree's Hairry","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1330560/f1a2d53cb93034aa637bffce3b6afe3ca0b24da4.jpg"},{"name":"Keys to the City","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1330560/5a8e60017776b3a9fc72af91f713086ed2a07100.jpg"},{"name":"The Hairytale","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1330560/ecd2beb858a11600f86e5a7bbec720d970bc5d4f.jpg"},{"name":"Cutting along","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/ste